HEADWORD: Carditis
<hw>Car*di"tis</hw> <pr>(k⟦aum⟧r*d⟦imac⟧"t⟦icr⟧s)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <grk>kardi`a</grk> heart +
